[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0951","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0951.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1110","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 Windows Media Player ActiveX 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.0 中集成的 Windows Media Player ActiveX 控件存在信息泄露漏洞。当远程攻击者通过恶意网页调用该控件访问客户端本地文件时，若文件不存在则返回特定错误码，攻击者可据此枚举目标系统上的文件是否存在，从而探测用户敏感文件信息。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 5.0 及关联的 Windows Media Player 组件，攻击者只需诱导用户访问恶意网页即可触发，无需任何身份认证。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1110"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:44.477","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 更高版本（如 IE 5.01 SP2 及以上）或改用现代浏览器（Edge/Chrome/Firefox）。如无法升级，可在 IE 中禁用 Windows Media Player ActiveX 控件：Internet 选项→安全→自定义级别→ActiveX 控件和插件→禁用\"对标记为可安全执行脚本的 ActiveX 控件执行脚本\"。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34675","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/793","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19618"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0951.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0951.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0951.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0901","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0901.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1050","title":"Matt Wright FormHandler.cgi 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Matt Wright FormHandler.cgi 2.0 存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过构造特制请求读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞利用方式有两种：一是通过 reply_message_attach 附件参数注入 \"..\"（点号）路径穿越序列，二是通过指定文件名作为模板进行文件读取。攻击者成功利用后可窃取敏感配置文件、密码文件或其他机密数据。该漏洞影响所有使用 FormHandler.cgi 2.0 版本的网站，由于 CGI 脚本通常以 Web 服务器权限运行，攻击者可能进一步获取服务器系统信息，威胁范围较广。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1050"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.070","remediation":"升级 Matt Wright FormHandler.cgi 至修复后版本（2.0 之后官方补丁版），或移除该 CGI 脚本改用受控表单处理组件；在 Web 服务器中限制 CGI 脚本仅可访问自身目录并禁用用户上传/指定附件文件名，使用 chroot 或 open_basedir 限制脚本文件读取范围，并对 reply_message_attach 参数做路径遍历过滤（拦截 ../ 及绝对路径），作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34600","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34939","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/798","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/799","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3550","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19620","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/50cb0f51a2a6988cb2c3b9e8c611d8b1e75d6a00/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1050.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1050","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1050.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/419b5e73717835e3c91c8f5fe969933e4b2e142e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1050.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6da213119b3c54637329347c0dc42c66b8a84f0a/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rrx8-7p59-h436/GHSA-rrx8-7p59-h436.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/798/info.html","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/formhandler.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1050.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0901.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0901.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0901.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1987","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1987.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1539","title":"QPC Software QVT/Term Plus 与 QVT/Net FTP 服务器 远程缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"QPC Software QVT/Term Plus 4.2d、4.3 及 QVT/Net 4.3 套件中的 FTP 服务器存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过发送超长的用户名或密码字符串触发该漏洞，导致服务拒绝，甚至可能在目标系统上执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 QVT/Term Plus 及 QVT/Net 套件的特定版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，属于高危漏洞。攻击条件仅需网络访问 FTP 服务端口，无需认证即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1539"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-11-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:40.440","remediation":"建议立即升级 QPC Software QVT/Term Plus 至 4.3 以上版本或 QVT/Net 4.3 以上版本，或联系厂商获取 FTP 服务缓冲区溢出补丁。如暂无法升级，请在防火墙层面限制 FTP 服务（TCP 21 端口）仅允许可信 IP 访问，并禁用匿名 FTP 登录作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94225924803704&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=94223972910670&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/796","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3491","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19619","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/49836c1c79a31c6cbe258de560530ef5be1db5f4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1539.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1539","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1539.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/36499b7630ab4a32d11ab7c901b4c87271211bec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1539.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b1dd20ab76cf8f3afbe611ea8133362b0532868d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2w9w-5m28-9576/GHSA-2w9w-5m28-9576.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1539.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/796/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0f9fb63c-ab1e-47c2-85e2-7b7de06d316c.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1987.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1000","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1000.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0837","title":"ISC BIND 8.2/8.2.1 TCP Session 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"ISC BIND 8.2 及 8.2.1 版本在处理 TCP 会话时存在拒绝服务漏洞，因未能正确关闭设置了 SO_LINGER 选项的 TCP 连接（improperly closing TCP sessions via so_linger）。远程攻击者可通过向运行 BIND 的 DNS 服务器发起大量特制的 TCP 会话连接，利用 SO_LINGER 套接字选项触发资源耗尽或非正常会话关闭逻辑，导致 named 守护进程崩溃或停止响应，造成 DNS 服务不可用。该漏洞影响使用 BIND 8.2 与 8.2.1 版本的 DNS 服务器，攻击者仅需网络可达目标 53 端口（TCP）即可实施攻击，无需身份认证，CVSS 评分达 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0837"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:09.680","remediation":"立即将 ISC BIND 升级至 8.2.2 或更高版本，该版本已修复 TCP 会话处理中 so_linger 使用不当导致的拒绝服务问题。如无法立即升级，可在 named.conf 中限制允许建立 TCP 区传送连接的客户端（allow-transfer），并在边界防火墙对 DNS 服务器 53 端口的 TCP 连接数做限速与并发限制，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/194","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/788","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a3a08d51f200d453300fca8b852aada6b8c5985a/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0837.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0837","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0837.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/44e56ab96b4cc04024678e20a1f15145c3b3cc59/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0837.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b1dd20ab76cf8f3afbe611ea8133362b0532868d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-x45h-gg4p-4cwx/GHSA-x45h-gg4p-4cwx.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/bind_vulnerable.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0837.json","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19991116.data"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1000.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0909","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0909.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0835","title":"ISC BIND 域名服务器 SIG 记录拒绝服务漏洞","description":"ISC BIND 8.2.2p1 及之前版本的 named 守护进程在处理 DNSSEC SIG 记录时存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者可发送包含畸形 SIG 记录的恶意 DNS 查询包，导致 named 进程崩溃或停止响应，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 BIND 8.x 系列 DNS 服务器，攻击者无需认证即可远程触发，仅需向目标 DNS 服务器发送精心构造的包含无效 SIG 记录的数据包即可利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级为严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0835"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:09.437","remediation":"建议立即安装 BIND 8.2.2p2 或更高版本的安全补丁，以修复 SIG 记录解析缺陷。如无法立即升级，可临时配置 `options { rate-limit {} };` 以限制查询速率，并通过防火墙过滤异常的 SIG 记录流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/788","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a3a08d51f200d453300fca8b852aada6b8c5985a/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0835.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0835","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0835.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/44e56ab96b4cc04024678e20a1f15145c3b3cc59/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0835.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b1dd20ab76cf8f3afbe611ea8133362b0532868d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-r826-x842-4xg9/GHSA-r826-x842-4xg9.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/bind_vulnerable.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0835.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19991116.data"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0909.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0651","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0651.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0851","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9096,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10778}}","description":"Sun Solaris 操作系统自带的 BIND 域名服务（named）存在拒绝服务漏洞，其根源在于对 NAPTR（命名权威指针）类型 DNS 记录的处理逻辑存在缺陷。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需向运行 named 服务的目标主机发送特制的包含畸形 NAPTR 记录的 DNS 查询请求，即可触发服务异常并导致 named 进程崩溃或停止响应，从而造成 DNS 服务不可用。该漏洞影响配置了 BIND named 且启用 NAPTR 记录解析的 Solaris 系统，攻击条件仅为攻击者能够与目标主机的 DNS 服务（通常为 UDP/TCP 53 端口）进行网络连通，利用方式简单、可远程发起，会对依赖该 DNS 服务的网络环境造成拒绝服务影响。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0851"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-11-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:11.407","remediation":"升级 Solaris 系统至已修复该 BIND 缺陷的补丁集群（如 Solaris 2.6 的 105708、Solaris 7 的 106655 等对应版本），或升级 BIND 至 8.2.2-P5 及以上版本。临时缓解措施：在 named 配置中限制递归查询来源，并通过防火墙阻断外部对 53 端口的 naptr 查询访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/194","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/788","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8cc4bd87e08227d0a597e9249036a66efd1a35dd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0851.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0851","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0851.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a5bae259b1f96bb239cbfd83cd9b28dd6d9df406/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0851.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-ghhr-vgwv-v39j/GHSA-ghhr-vgwv-v39j.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/bind_vulnerable.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0851.json","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19991116.data"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0651.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0649","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0649.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0849","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9120,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":10804}}","description":"ISC BIND 8.2.1 及之前版本在处理 DNS 查询时存在拒绝服务漏洞。其 named 服务在解析包含超长域名（超过 maxdname 限制）的数据包时，因对域名长度校验不当，会触发内部处理异常。未经过身份认证的远程攻击者只需向目标 DNS 服务器发送精心构造的畸形 DNS 请求，即可导致 named 进程崩溃或停止响应，使域名解析服务中断。该漏洞影响运行 ISC BIND 8.2.1 及以下版本且暴露在网络中的 DNS 服务器，攻击条件仅需网络可达目标 53 端口，无需任何权限，利用方式简单，常被用于分布式拒绝服务攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0849"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:11.170","remediation":"建议将 ISC BIND 升级至 8.2.2 或更高版本以修复 maxdname 处理缺陷导致的拒绝服务问题。如暂时无法升级，应通过防火墙或 ACL 限制仅允许可信主机访问 named 服务的 53 端口（TCP/UDP），并在 named.conf 中配置 allow-query/allow-recursion 收紧递归查询权限，同时关闭不必要的区域传送。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/194","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/788","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/68b3c685b96421db99cac9beb9d7bc8a6314be79/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0849.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0849","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0849.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/36499b7630ab4a32d11ab7c901b4c87271211bec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0849.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/645f3b3aab113438413618cef41319453f39d643/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-4hq8-3ffh-25xf/GHSA-4hq8-3ffh-25xf.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/bind_vulnerable.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0849.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0649.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0649.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0647","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0647.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0848","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9172,\"outputTokens\":30,\"totalTokens\":10866}}","description":"ISC BIND 8.2 及 8.2.1 版本的 named 服务在处理客户端请求时，未能正确限制单个进程所打开的文件描述符数量，存在\"fdmax\"文件描述符耗尽缺陷。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可向目标 DNS 服务器持续发起大量连接请求，使 named 进程消耗超过 fdmax 限制的文件描述符，导致服务无法接受新连接而拒绝服务。该漏洞影响运行 BIND 8.2/8.2.1 的 DNS 服务器（包括 IRIX 6.5.17、Solaris 7.0 等平台），攻击仅需网络可达目标 53 端口即可发起，无需任何权限，属于远程拒绝服务类漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0848"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:11.040","remediation":"建议将 ISC BIND 升级至 8.2.2 或更高版本（官方已在 8.2.2 中修复 fdmax 文件描述符耗尽问题）。若无法立即升级，可在 named 配置中调低 options 块的 fdmax 限制，并通过防火墙限制仅允许受信任的递归客户端访问 53 端口，以减少被耗尽文件描述符的攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/194","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/788","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19615","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/68b3c685b96421db99cac9beb9d7bc8a6314be79/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0848.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0848","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0848.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/36499b7630ab4a32d11ab7c901b4c87271211bec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0848.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/645f3b3aab113438413618cef41319453f39d643/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-pvjg-h4mg-c3q7/GHSA-pvjg-h4mg-c3q7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/bind_vulnerable.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0848.json","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19991116.data"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0647.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0647.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0618","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0618.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0833","title":"Solaris BIND 8.2 中高级网络服务软件的缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"BIND 8.2 版本在处理 DNS 区域文件中的 NXT（Next Domain）资源记录时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当 BIND 服务器解析包含特制超长或畸形 NXT 记录的域名数据时，由于未对记录长度进行边界校验，会导致内存缓冲区被覆盖。远程攻击者可通过向运行 BIND 8.2 的 DNS 服务器发送精心构造的 NXT 记录查询或响应，触发该溢出，进而造成服务崩溃（拒绝服务）或在特定条件下执行任意代码。该漏洞主要影响使用 BIND 8.2 的 Solaris 及其他类 Unix 系统，攻击无需身份认证，仅需网络可达目标 DNS 服务即可发起。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0833"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:09.190","remediation":"建议升级 BIND 至 8.2.3 或更高版本（如 BIND 9.x），或升级 Solaris 至修复该漏洞的补丁版本（如 Solaris 8 10/00 及后续补丁）。临时缓解措施：在防火墙层面限制非授权 IP 访问 DNS 服务（TCP/UDP 53 端口），或在 named.conf 中禁用 DNSSEC/NXT 记录处理功能。建议尽快升级至 BIND 9.2.0 或更高版本彻底修复该 NXT 记录缓冲区溢出漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/788","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f56f639de76f94fc0aef783754a3de16fea7357b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0833.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0833","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0833.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/be19cdaa6196942fd4096a42a1eaf047a8584298/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0833.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/259.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/dns.rules","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b1dd20ab76cf8f3afbe611ea8133362b0532868d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-3q86-gfmq-f6c6/GHSA-3q86-gfmq-f6c6.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/B/bind_vulnerable.nasl","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.169"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0618.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0618.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1142","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1142.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1511","title":"Artisoft XtraMail POP3/SMTP及Control Service缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"XtraMail 1.11 存在多处缓冲区溢出漏洞，涉及 POP3、SMTP 及 Control Service 三个服务组件。远程未经认证的攻击者可通过向 POP3 服务发送超长 PASS 命令、向 SMTP 服务发送超长 HELO 命令、或在 Control Service 中提交超长用户名，触发缓冲区溢出，导致目标服务进程崩溃（拒绝服务），在特定条件下还可利用该漏洞执行任意代码。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1511"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-10","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"XtraMail 已停止维护多年，官方未发布安全补丁。建议立即迁移至现代邮件服务器软件（如 hMailServer、Dovecot、Postfix 等）。临时缓解措施：在防火墙严格限制对 POP3（110）、SMTP（25）及 Control Service（32000）端口的访问，仅允许受信 IP 连接，并部署入侵检测系统监控异常长命令数据包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94226003804744&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/791","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3488"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1142.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1520","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1520.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0985","title":"CGI City CC Whois 1.0 远程命令注入漏洞","description":"CGI City 的 CC Whois 1.0 程序中的 whois.cgi 存在命令注入漏洞，其根源在于程序未对用户输入的域名参数进行任何过滤或转义，便直接拼接至系统 Shell 命令中执行。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需向 whois.cgi 提交包含 Shell 元字符（如分号、管道符、反引号等）的恶意域名查询请求，即可在目标 Web 服务器上执行任意操作系统命令。该漏洞影响所有运行 CC Whois 1.0 的服务器，成功利用可导致服务器被远程控制、敏感数据泄露或拒绝服务，CVSS 评分为 7.5，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0985"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:27.850","remediation":"tags.<value>升级到最新版 CC Whois 1.5+，使用安全解析函数替代 shell_exec，并在 web 根目录禁用执行权限；如无法立即更新，可使用 waf 规则过滤包含特殊字符的域名参数作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0985","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20433","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-0985.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad08212eac84f46206c2da8a50436d48e5ad608c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0985.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0985","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHears