或更高版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1111"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:44.603","remediation":"立即升级至 StackGuard 1.21 或更高版本，该版本引入 XOR 随机金丝雀机制，将返回地址与随机金丝雀值绑定，使攻击者无法在不破坏金丝雀的情况下直接修改返回地址指针。软件可从 http://immunix.org/downloads.html#sg1.21 获取。同时建议开发者避免在同一函数中同时使用 gets() 类溢出函数和指针间接写入操作。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94218618329838&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/786","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3524","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e25ede9c3545efaa8ff0b393e30e48edb07502a8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1111.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1111","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1111.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1111.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fpjr-9gj6-mc3v/GHSA-fpjr-9gj6-mc3v.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1111.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000868.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5fd10034-0e95-458a-8e9d-f6ddb2de6532.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_ex